SUPLINF.P:
Section 2904 of the Food, Conservation, and Energy Act of 2008 (2008 Act) requires that implementation of programs authorized by Title II of the 2008 Act be made without regard to the Paperwork Reduction Act of 1995 (44 U.S.C. 3501 
et seq.
). Therefore, NRCS is not reporting recordkeeping or estimated paperwork burden associated with this final rule.
